'''''Benar''''' were a pair of [[Modular conveyor]]s belonging to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]]. ''Benar'' group were part of the [[Imperial II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial II''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Corrupter (Imperial-class)|''Corrupter'']]{{'s}} [[Corrupter repair convoy|vital resupply convoy]] lead by the [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|''Nebulon-B'' Frigate]] [[Monitor (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|''Monitor'']] to the ''Corrupter'' in the [[Mev system/Legends|Mev system]]. Both of their cargoes were 'provisions'. The ships were then attacked by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] raiders and was destroyed.

